===============================
Sale Order Line Duplication
===============================

.. !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
   !! This file is generated by amzsys-gen-addon-readme !!
   !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!
   !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!


This module allows you to create duplicate sale order line.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

To use this module, you need to:

#. Make a sale order with products.
#. Save the sale order line.
#. Click on the Duplicate button inorder to create duplicate sale order line record.
#. Duplicate record will be generated as the last record.
#. This record will be automatically saved in database.

Known issues / Roadmap
======================

- Modifiying the original demand after the forcing could lead to misscalculations.

